  <div class="contentPadding">
  
  <div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">Elected officials running campaigns is not served time</div>
  <table width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top">
    <div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3959-4049">Josh Senecal</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div>
    </td>
    <td align="right">
      





    <div>
      


      

      
        <span id="FlagIdea"><a class="iconLink" href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('FlagIdea', '/akira/flagDiscussionTopic.do?ID=3189')"><img alt="Warning" class="iconLink" src="/images/iconshock/warning_16.gif" border="0">&nbsp;Flag</a></span>
      

      

    </div>

    </td>
  </tr>
  </table>
    


  <div id="DiscussionTopicText_3189">
    





  <div style="float:left; margin:3px;">
      <div id="DiscussionTopicVote_3189">
        <div id="IdeaScale_Vote" align="center"><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_3189', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2247&topicID=3189&vote=1')"><img alt="Vote Up" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_up.gif"/>&nbsp;Looks Promising!</a></div><div style="padding:5px;font-size:2em"><a onmouseout="setTimeout('Bubble.hide()', 500)" onmouseover="Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 3 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 26</div><div>Votes Against : 6</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_3189'))" style="text-decoration:none;" id="TopicVote_3189" href="javascript:Bubble.showTip('<div>Idea Created : 3 days ago</div><div>Votes For : 26</div><div>Votes Against : 6</div>', document.getElementById('TopicVote_3189'))">20</a></div><div style="padding:3px"><a href="javascript:ajaxInlinePopup('DiscussionTopicVote_3189', '/akira/discussionVote.do?dbid=2247&topicID=3189&vote=-1')"><img alt="Vote Down" border="0" style="vertical-align:middle" src="/images/ideascale/vote_down.gif"/>&nbsp;I'm Not So Sure...</a></div></div>
      </div>  
  </div>

  


  Elected officials running campaigns should not be paid for time in office.<br/><br/>Elected politicians running campaigns (for long periods of time) while in office for other positions are not doing the job paid for it, seems appreciate and fair that any person paid by the people should either:<br/><br/>-leave office to campaign.<br/>-receive no pay while not on duty.<br/>-serve the time lost serving.<br/><br/>

  <h3>Why Is This Idea Important?</h3><div></div>

  </div>

  <div style="clear:both"><div>

  <div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;">Idea # 592</span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3189"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2247">Between Federal, State, and Local Governments</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=campaigns paid taxes">campaigns paid taxes</a></span></div>  

  


  <div id="IdeaScale_SectionHeader">Comments</div>  

  


